{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"21f9b12d0b","title":"对电力工业的第二个五年计划的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0bcb5043c3","index":0,"year":1958,"month":4,"day":25,"articleId":"21f9b12d0b"}],"tags":[{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji39","name":"毛泽东全集第39卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/39-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji39":{"comments":[{"id":"0c3063c3c3","publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"21f9b12d0b","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指水利电力部向中共中央政治局报送的关于电力工业的第二个五年计划。主要内容包括：（一）加快电力工业发展速度，十年赶上英国。（二）发挥地方积极性，促进全国电气化。（三）放手发动群众，全民办电。（四）水电和火电的比重。（五）电力网建设。（六）设备供应问题。（七）投资问题。"}],"contents":[{"id":"5718ae2af8","type":"title","text":"对电力工业的第二个五年计划的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"21f9b12d0b"},{"id":"0c3063c3c3","type":"paragraph","text":"此件写得很好。有了正确的政治观点，从政治上想通了，政治统师了业务，迷信破除，胸怀坦荡，势如破竹了。除了已经写了较好报告的几个部以外，希望各部仿照几个好的报告写一个或长或短的报告给我和政治局各同志。如有好文章，可写上万把字。要条理清整，政治统师，思想明确，文学生动","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"21f9b12d0b"},{"id":"727cac33d8","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"21f9b12d0b"},{"id":"7d1410c1c5","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五八年四月廿五日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"21f9b12d0b"}],"page":{"id":"6f5c420600","publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"21f9b12d0b","start":255,"end":255}}}},"__N_SSG":true}